  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5134088/" class="title-link">慈禧仅仅是一个阴谋家</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5134088"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/55337678/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55337678/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">怀念你柔情似水</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-10-17"
      class="main-meta">2011-10-17 10:39:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5134088_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  慈禧仅仅是一个阴谋家 不是一个合格政治家 她没有政治家思想和个性，各种思想自相矛盾不足为奇。居然有人说他把晚清推迟了几年灭亡是功绩。 可笑啊，她把中国的末世延长了这么多年，不说百姓苦，只说历史。结合当时的世界环境，如果早10年结束清朝，或许中国也不会被日本按在胯...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5134088/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5134088_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5134088_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





